extends layout.pug
block links
    link(rel="stylesheet" href="dist/css/login.css")
block content
    div.d-flex.align-items-center.justify-content-center#mydiv
        form.login-form.p-4
            .row
                .col-4.d-flex.align-items-center
                    i(class="fas fa-address-card text-primary")
                .col-8    
                    .form-group
                        input(type="email" class="form-control" id="exampleInputEmail1" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Endereço de Email")
                        small(id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted") Digite seu endereço de email para acessar o sistema.
                    .form-group
                        input(type="password" class="form-control" id="exampleInputPassword1" placeholder="Senha de Acesso")
                    button(type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100") Acessar o Sistema